2009;;Opie Gets Laid;;American;;James Ricardo;;April Wade, Ute Werner, Jesselynn Desmond, James Ricardo, Gina DeVettori;;comedy;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Opie_Gets_Laid;;At 30 years old, Opie (James Ricardo) is a virgin whose existence is made up of watching pornography and eating junk food. One day a drug dealer named Thai (April Wade) mistakenly comes to his door. She decides to help Opie by finding him a good woman, initially (and unsuccessfully) by online personal ads. Thai and Opie end up sleeping together while high on marijuana, and then end up seeing each other regularly. Opie starts having sex with other women, including Thai's lesbian lover Dakota (Ute Werner) and a "gun-toting" nymphomaniac named Rain (Jesselynn Desmond).